OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772136279
OL,3,CParents promised that police will
OL,4,Ccorrect Hillsborough legal record
OL,6,FThe parents of two teenagers who were
OL,7,Fkilled in the Hillsborough disaster
OL,8,Fhave been promised the legal record
OL,9,Fabout how their daughters died will be
OL,10,Fcorrected.
OL,12,FJenni and Trevor Hicks lost both of
OL,13,Ftheir daughters, Sarah, aged 19, and
OL,14,FVictoria, aged 15, at Hillsborough in
OL,15,F1989.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
