CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772136279
OL,3,CParents promised that police will
OL,4,Ccorrect Hillsborough legal record
OL,6,FTheir civil case in the early 1990s
OL,7,Fwas dismissed on the basis that the
OL,8,Fgirls were assumed to have been
OL,9,Funconscious within seconds and died
OL,10,Fshortly afterwards, findings that
OL,11,Flater inquiries and inquests
OL,12,Fdemonstrated were fundamentally flawed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772136279
OL,3,CParents promised that police will
OL,4,Ccorrect Hillsborough legal record
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police Chief Constable
OL,7,FLauren Poultney met Mr and Mrs Hicks
OL,8,Ffor the first time and confirmed that
OL,9,Fshe had instructed the force's legal
OL,10,Fteam to proceed with a 'Statement in
OL,11,FOpen Court' (SOAC) acknowledging that
OL,12,Fearlier court findings about the
OL,13,Fdeaths of their daughters should be
OL,14,Fcorrected.
OL,16,FIt comes following recent criticism of
OL,17,Fthe police for failing to discuss the
OL,18,Fdisputed legal record, despite
OL,19,Frepeated requests by lawyers
OL,20,Frepresenting the Hicks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
