CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772136279
OL,3,CParents promised that police will
OL,4,Ccorrect Hillsborough legal record
OL,6,FA statement in open court is a
OL,7,Frecognised legal mechanism used to
OL,8,Fformally correct the public record `
OL,9,Fbut SYP's refusal to do so has led to
OL,10,Fintense criticism in recent weeks,
OL,11,Fincluding from the Mayor of Greater
OL,12,FManchester Andy Burnham and the former
OL,13,FPrime Minister Theresa May.
OL,15,FFollowing the meeting, Jenni Hicks
OL,16,Fsaid: "This is the first time we have
OL,17,Fsat down with a Chief Constable and
OL,18,Fbeen told directly that steps will be
OL,19,Ftaken to correct the record about our
OL,20,Fdaughters.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772136279
OL,3,CParents promised that police will
OL,4,Ccorrect Hillsborough legal record
OL,6,F"We welcome what we have been told
OL,7,Ftoday, and we are pleased that South
OL,8,FYorkshire Police appears to recognise
OL,9,Fthat this needs to be put right.
OL,11,F"But after everything families have
OL,12,Fbeen through over the past 36 years,
OL,13,Fwe will wait to see it happen in open
OL,14,Fcourt before celebrating."
OL,16,FTrevor Hicks added: "Today felt like a
OL,17,Fhugely important step forward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772136279
OL,3,CParents promised that police will
OL,4,Ccorrect Hillsborough legal record
OL,6,F"We have waited a very long time to
OL,7,Fhear these words from the leadership
OL,8,Fof South Yorkshire Police. What
OL,9,Fmatters now is that the promise made
OL,10,Ftoday is followed through."
OL,12,FThe commitment follows years of legal
OL,13,Fefforts by the Hicks family to correct
OL,14,Fcourt rulings which still state that
OL,15,Ftheir daughters experienced "swift and
OL,16,Fsudden" deaths, despite medical
OL,17,Fevidence heard at later Hillsborough
OL,18,Fproceedings showing that many victims
OL,19,Fremained conscious for significantly
OL,20,Flonger.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772136279
OL,3,CParents promised that police will
OL,4,Ccorrect Hillsborough legal record
OL,6,FNia Williams, acting for Jenni and
OL,7,FTrevor, said: "Jenni Hicks and Trevor
OL,8,FHicks were today able to look the
OL,9,FChief Constable in the eye and explain
OL,10,Fwhy this legal correction is so
OL,11,Fimportant.
OL,13,F"We are pleased that the Chief
OL,14,FConstable has confirmed that she has
OL,15,Finstructed SYP's legal team to agree
OL,16,Fto the Statement in Open Court and we
OL,17,Fhope that will happen very soon."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
