FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772136279
OL,3,CParents promised that police will
OL,4,Ccorrect Hillsborough legal record
OL,6,FThe development also follows a House
OL,7,Fof Lords event which examined how
OL,8,Fvictims can, in future, correct
OL,9,Fhistoric judicial records - a 'Hicks'
OL,10,FRule - when later evidence overturns
OL,11,Fthe factual basis on which earlier
OL,12,Frulings were made. Currently it
OL,13,Frequires the consent of the wrongdoer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
